; Coverage for commodity.cc tag presence comparison
; One lot with tag, other without - tests the asymmetric tag paths
; The lot without tag sorts first

2024/01/01 Buy
    Assets:Brokerage    10 AAPL {$150.00} (lot1)
    Assets:Checking

2024/01/15 Buy More
    Assets:Brokerage    5 AAPL {$150.00}
    Assets:Checking

test bal --lots Assets:Brokerage
       5 AAPL {$150}
10 AAPL {$150} (lot1)  Assets:Brokerage
end test
